{"type":"miscellaneous","title":"Fireblossom","summaries":["<b>Fireblossom</b> is a type of herb which appears as a small, magma-colored flower. It grows on Ash Blocks in The Underworld and can be cut with virtually any weapon or tool. It can also be planted in Clay Pots, Planter Boxes, or on Ash Blocks using Fireblossom Seeds.","<span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> Fireblossoms will bloom when the sun is setting, from 3:45 pm to 7:30 pm, unless it is raining. Both the Fireblossom and its respective seeds have a chance to be obtained from the Herb Bag. It will only drop seeds while blooming and like any other herb will drop 1-3.","Like the Fireblossom Seeds, this item is immune to lava despite being white rarity.","<span class=\"eico i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> Fireblossoms require that they are at least partially submerged in lava to bloom, but will bloom any time of day once they are submerged."],"statistics":{"Max stack":"999 <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 99 <span class=\"eico s i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>","Rarity":"<span class=\"rarity\">[img:Rarity level: 0]</span>","Sell":"<span class=\"coin\" title=\"20 Copper Coins\" data-sort-value=\"20\"><span class=\"cc\">20</span></span>","Research":"<abbr class=\"journey\" title=\"Journey Mode\">25 required</abbr>"},"crafts":{"Used in":[{"result":{"rowspan":1,"value":"<span class=\"i multi-line\">[img:Garland]<span><span>Garland</span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span></span>"},"ingredients":{"value":"<ul><li><span class=\"i\">[img:Daybloom]<span><span>Daybloom</span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"i\">[img:Moonglow]<span><span>Moonglow</span></span></span></li><li><span class=\